---
import OutreachListLayout from '../layouts/OutreachListLayout.astro';
---

<OutreachListLayout
  title="Outreach | Wavey Dynamics"
  heading="OUTREACH"
  subheading="Community outreach activities."
  description="Wavey Dynamics community outreach — visiting schools, exhibitions and media to inspire the next generation into STEM careers through the platform of motorsport."
>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">The importance of inspiring a diverse talent base in our future generation of engineers can't be neglected.</p>
  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">We have visited several schools and exhibitions around London and the South East to demonstrate what engineers do, the possibilities ahead of them and even made some educational games to demonstrate some basic scientific principles.</p>
  <p class="mb-12 leading-relaxed">We have also made appearances on media outlets such as Sky Sports to discuss what we are doing within the motorsport space and some of the initiatives we have developed to drive change in our industry.</p>

  <div class="space-y-14">

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Mission44 x Motorsport UK: Race for Diversity</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">As part of a collaboration between Mission 44 and Motorsport UK, Wavey Dynamics was asked to develop an activation aimed at engaging and inspiring children aged 11–14 into STEM careers through the platform of motorsport.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[242px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/outreach-mission44.jpg" alt="Mission44 x Motorsport UK" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Sky Sports</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">As part of a Sky Sports feature on Black figures in motorsport for Black History Month, our director Jahee had an appearance alongside driver Sara Misir where he talked about some of our initiatives and ambitions within the motorsport and high performance engineering space.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[242px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/outreach-skysports.png" alt="Sky Sports" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Black STEAM @ Birmingham Science Museum</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">As part of The Black STEAM event, organised by Brit Pact, we were invited to talk to children &amp; young people on the opportunities in STEM careers open to them through the platform of motorsport.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[242px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/outreach-blacksteam-2.jpg" alt="Black STEAM @ Birmingham Science Museum" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Haberdashers' Aske's Knights Academy</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">Routes into Engineering: A talk with Year 8 and 9 students on the occupation of engineering, explaining the different engineering disciplines and our role in today's society. We also discussed what kinds of projects they may be lucky enough to work on if they choose to pursue further education, followed by a Q&amp;A session.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[242px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/outreach-haberdashers.jpg" alt="Haberdashers' Aske's Knights Academy" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Holmleigh Primary School</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">In March 2019 our director Jahee visited Holmleigh Primary school in East London with friend and colleague Dan Basha to give a talk to Year 1 students (Age 5-6) on some simple engineering concepts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[242px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/outreach-holmleigh.png" alt="Holmleigh Primary School" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Brighton &amp; Hove Motor Show</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">Wavey Dynamics kicked off a community outreach program with an exhibition at Brighton &amp; Hove's first annual Motor Show in June 2017.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[242px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/outreach-brighton.jpg" alt="Brighton &amp; Hove Motor Show" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</OutreachListLayout>
